<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之後我也想<delay8 />幫房間<delay8 />換個擺設，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我就觀摩一下你的房間<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當作參考囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
原來你每天<delay8 />都是生活在這裡啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />能更加了解<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />一點，<delay20 />
我總覺得好開心喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
你的房間真是充滿了巧思呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能布置成這種感覺真不錯，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我都有點羨慕了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說房間裡的壁紙<delay8 />或是窗簾，<delay20 />
好像會讓空間的感覺大幅改變呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要不要也把房間<delay8 />
布置成這種感覺呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你的房間<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總讓人覺得很安心呢～<delay frames="40" />
我都有點不想回去了<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 />真對不起！<delay frames="40" />
我沒有要賴著不走的意思！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請放心吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然我們難得聚在一起，<delay20 />
不如就來開個朗讀會吧？來唸這本……<delay20 />
《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />》！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我本來<delay8 />是這麼想的啦，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但因為是臨時起意，<delay20 />
我沒有把書帶來呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這間房間真是充滿了<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的風格呢！<pageBreak />為了培養這樣的品味，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><gender3 m="他" f="她" />是不是<delay8 />
平常就很花心思注意了呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />也真是的，<delay20 />
只要待在自己的家裡，<delay8 />
就真的很放鬆呢。
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過這間房間<delay8 />的確會讓人
覺得平靜呢，真是不可思議～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />連我也覺得<delay8 />非常放鬆喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="101_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果什麼家具都不放，<delay8 />
房間看起來就會很寬敞呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡將來<delay8 />
會變成哪種風格的房間呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺會有無限的可能喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這麼方便用吸塵器打掃的房間，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我<delay8 />有點羨慕呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
